addTaglet

protected void addTaglet(String name,
                         String key)
Adds the specified taglet to the list of taglets to be sorted.

The taglet is added according to the ".before", ".after" and ".between" keys in the configuration passed to the sorter at creation time.

Parameters:
name - the name of the taglet to add.
key - the lookup key prefix in the configuration to use.
Since:
1.5.0
